GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_TwoPurchaseTriggers> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_TwoPurchaseTriggers> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TwoPurchaseTriggers> ;
    narr:childCount "3"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "ad01b8eca10108d9161cacb5d1e0d4d387be5b6a" ;
    narr:narration """The market segmentation model initially posited two distinct purchase triggers: the [solo professional](narr:Position_Trigger1SoloProfessional), whose daily need for context-aware AI output drives individual-tier adoption, and the [delegator](narr:Position_Trigger2Delegator), a high-stakes archetype seeking to scale expertise across teams. While these triggers framed early market entry, recent evidence suggests a shift in how value is communicated. The [current perspective](narr:Narrative_ShowVsDemoProof) challenges the necessity of hands-on trials for initial proof, arguing that value is fully demonstrable through clear, high-fidelity showing rather than requiring the user to input their own data. This reframes the 'try-it' requirement as a potential hedge, suggesting that 'their-own-data' is a conversion deepener rather than the primary mechanism for establishing initial value.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ShowVsDemoProof> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_Trigger1SoloProfessional> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_Trigger2Delegator> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Information isn't enough to do your work. You need perspective. So does your AI." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_Trigger1SoloProfessional> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Stop being the bottleneck. Install your expertise so your team can work without you." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_Trigger2Delegator> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Value is proven by showing clearly; their-own-data is the conversion deepener, not the proof" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ShowVsDemoProof> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The 'show-don't-try' model contradicts the earlier assumption that hands-on data integration is required to bridge the activation gap." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ShowVsDemoProof> ] ;
    narr:writer "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite" .
}